# Rust build output
/target

# The linked Lean static archive (~246 MB) — a derived build artifact (the full native
# transitive closure of the compiled Metatheory + mathlib). Regenerate it from the Lean
# build; do NOT commit it.
*.a
*.o
# Archive backups produced when re-splicing the native closure (e.g. before adding a new
# @[export]); large derived artifacts, never committed.
*.a.bak
*.bak
